    <item>
      <title>斯塔默向政治低头，任命摩根·麦克斯威尼为其首席助手</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/who-is-morgan-mcsweeney-and-why-did-uk-s-starmer-back-him-over-sue-gray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯尔·斯塔默执政的前三个月过得并不顺利，他的政府饱受捐款争议、内讧和英国公共财政日益低迷的困扰。周日，他终于向工党压倒性胜利的缔造者求助，试图纠正局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/who-is-morgan-mcsweeney-and-why-did-uk-s-starmer-back-him-over-sue-gray</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lululemon 创始人价值 6000 万美元的房子因选举标志被毁坏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁 Lululemon Athletica Inc. 创始人奇普·威尔逊 (Chip Wilson) 价值 6000 万美元的豪宅已成为涂满涂鸦的导火索，象征着加拿大省级选举的两极分化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/lululemon-founder-s-60-million-house-defaced-in-british-columbia-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>突尼斯总统连任失败 投票率低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/tunisia-president-kais-saied-wins-reelection-with-90-7-of-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯总统凯斯·赛义德在一场遭到超过三分之二合格选民冷遇的选举中赢得第二任期，因为在这个阿拉伯之春起义的发源地，人们对他的独裁统治方式日益不满。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/tunisia-president-kais-saied-wins-reelection-with-90-7-of-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:23:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的税收计划因竞选承诺遭遇现实而受挫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当英国首相凯尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 和财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 策划工党在英国的执政之路时，他们希望通过提高私募股权和超级富豪“非本地”居民的税收来为关键支出计划提供资金。现在，这些承诺正在变成现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/reeves-s-tax-plans-falter-as-election-pledges-meet-reality</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:12:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟贷款部门提议通过 IPO 投资促进市场联盟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-lending-arm-proposes-ipo-investments-to-foster-markets-union</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟贷款机构正在制定计划，促进欧盟境内企业上市，这是降低资本壁垒和提高竞争力的努力之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/eu-lending-arm-proposes-ipo-investments-to-foster-markets-union</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 18:12:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会提起的亚马逊反垄断诉讼在裁决后将取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-antitrust-case-filed-by-ftc-to-move-forward-after-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司必须面对美国联邦贸易委员会就其在线市场提起的反垄断诉讼，但联邦法官驳回了该机构与州消费者保护法相关的一些指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/amazon-antitrust-case-filed-by-ftc-to-move-forward-after-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 17:25:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚副总统反对弹劾，不会辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚副总统里加蒂·加查瓜 (Rigathi Gachagua) 表示，他将于周二出席国民议会，就违反宪法的指控为自己进行弹劾辩护，并拒绝辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/kenya-s-deputy-president-to-fight-impeachment-in-parliament</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:46:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥市长对资金短缺的学区董事会进行改组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊周一宣布了该市公立学校董事会的新成员名单。上周，约翰逊表示，由于预算短缺引发的紧张局势加剧，他之前任命的所有董事会成员都将辞职。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/chicago-mayor-appoints-a-new-school-board-in-latest-upheaval</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 16:23:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称在战争一周年之际拦截了哈马斯火箭弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军称，他们拦截了伊朗支持的哈马斯向特拉维夫发射的大部分火箭弹，经过一年的战争，双方的战斗于周一进一步升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/israel-says-it-intercepted-hamas-rockets-as-war-marks-one-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 15:56:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博索纳罗支持的候选人在巴西大选中领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bolsonaro-backed-candidates-pull-ahead-in-brazil-mayor-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在被视为巴西政治情绪晴雨表的市政选举中，雅伊尔·博索纳罗支持的候选人领先，两年后将举行总统选举，路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦很可能会寻求连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bolsonaro-backed-candidates-pull-ahead-in-brazil-mayor-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 01:58:33 GMT</pubDate>
